message.body: Hey! I know it is late notice but any chance u want to grab a bite to eat? I was planning to pick up take out from Doma but could also eat there if u wanted to join.
I could at 6:45 if that works for you. But ONLY if you let me treat for #############!
That time works but no need to treat me. I invited you so you joining me is treat enough!
OK. Can you try to get a reservation just to be safe? I'll meet you there!
Sounds good! I'll call now. You sure it is not putting u out? I don't want you to have to rush. I know you've been really busy. We could always go another night if this isn't good.
Awesome! We're in for 6:45. See you there!
Be there in two mins. Res under my name.
